original_title: Queens: Marathon Parkway - Van Zandt Avenue
text:
Marathon Parkway, below Van Zandt Avenue, Little Neck, showing Frank Jackowski's place in the woods. Marathon Parkway was formerly Clinton Avenue.

P. L. Sperr

June 10, 1927
